30 Relating to the State Board of Chiropractic Examiners;
31 to amend Section 34-24-140, as last amended by Act 2025-335,
32 2025 Regular Session, and Section 34-24-160, Code of Alabama
33 1975, to revise the requirements for serving on the board; to
34 revise the qualifications that applicants must satisfy for
35 licensure; and to make nonsubstantive, technical revisions to
36 update the existing code language to current style
